            <li>Presidential Medal of Freedom (1956)</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="tribute-section">
        <h2>Legacy</h2>
        <p>John von Neumann's legacy is vast and enduring. His contributions have left an indelible mark on mathematics, computer science, and physics. He passed away on February 8, 1957, but his work continues to influence and inspire scientists and engineers around the world.</p>
